CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Ebang International Holdings Inc is an application-specific integrated circuit, or ASIC, chip design company and a manufacturer of high-performance Bitcoin mining machines. The company's Ebit E10 model, is a commercial mining machine that uses 10 nm ASIC chips among other mining machine producers. It operates in a single segment selling Bitcoin mining machines and related accessories, telecommunications products and provision of management and maintenance services.
